ats-producer-award-ukraine-1236212446%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Rift%20Grew%20Between%20AAP%20and%20Kailash%20Gahlot%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDelhi%20minister%20Kailash%20Gahlot's%20walkout%20from%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20was%20the%20culmination%20of%20a%20rift%20that%20had%20its%20genesis%20in%20the%20division%20of%20portfolios%20held%20by%20Manish%20Sisodia%20after%20he%20was%20arrested%20in%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20case.%20Mr%20Sisodia%2C%20then%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Delhi%2C%20held%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20portfolios%20-%2018%20--%20that%20not%20only%20included%20the%20flagship%20health%20and%20education%2C%20but%20also%20law%2C%20revenue%20and%20power%2C%20water%2C%20finance%20and%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20arrest%20in%20March%20last%20year%2C%20most%20of%20these%20portfolios%20were%20divided%20between%20Saurabh%20Bhardwaj%20and%20Atishi%2C%20who%20is%20now%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20the%20Law%20and%20Justice%20Department%20was%20taken%20away%20from%20Mr%20Gehlot%20and%20given%20to%20Atishi.%20People%20close%20to%20Mr%20Gahlot%20said%20it%20became%20clear%20then%20that%20the%20top%20leadership%20of%20the%20party%20does%20not%20have%20much%20confidence%20in%20Mr%20Gahlot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20beginning%20of%20Mr%20Gahlot's%20standoff%20with%20the%20current%20Chief%20Minister%20that%20suddenly%20came%20to%20public%20notice%20during%20the%20flag-hoisting%20ceremony%20of%20Independence%20Day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%2C%20who%20was%20in%20jail%20at%20the%20time%2C%20had%20delegated%20the%20task%20to%20Atishi%20-%20a%20choice%20that%20made%20clear%20her%20prominence%20in%20the%20party%20and%20sparked%20speculation%20that%20she%20might%20be%20the%20one%20to%20succeed%20him%20in%20the%20top%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena%2C%20however%20intervened%2C%20and%20handed%20the%20job%20to%20Mr%20Gahlot%2C%20who%20complied%20without%20any%20conciliatory%20words%20to%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20or%20Atishi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20resignation%20letter%2C%20Mr%20Gahlot%20has%20attributed%20his%20decision%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bdwindling%20credibility%26quot%3B%20of%20AAP%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20cleaning%20of%20Yamuna%20and%20'Sheeshmahal'%20-%20a%20pejorative%20term%20used%20by%20the%20BJP%20for%20the%20chief%20minister's%20renovated%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20AAP%20leader%20Sanjay%20Singh%20accused%20Mr%20Gehlot%20of%20reading%20the%20script%20of%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20has%20maintained%20silence%20on%20the%20resignation.%20At%20a%20press%20conference%20to%20welcome%20former%20BJP%20MLA%20Anil%20Jha%20to%20AAP%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20was%20asked%20about%20Mr%20Gehlot's%20sudden%20resignation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20refused%20to%20respond%2C%20passing%20the%20mic%20to%20senior%20party%20leader%20Durgesh%20Pathak%2C%20who%20was%20sitting%20next%20to%20him.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnMr%20Pathak%20said%20Kailash%20Gehlot%20was%20being%20questioned%20and%20raided%20by%20the%20ED%20and%20Income%20Tax%20Department%20for%20several%20months.%20Other%20party%20leaders%20had%20not%20minced%20words%2C%20saying%20openly%20that%20Mr%20Gahlot%20could%20not%20withstand%20the%20pressure%20and%20decided%20to%20go%20with%20the%20flow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKailash%20Gehlot%20was%20being%20pressurised%20through%20ED-CBI%20raids%20and%20he%20is%20speaking%20according%20to%20BJP's%20script.%20Modi%20washing%20machine%20has%20started%20working%20before%20the%20Delhi%20elections.%20Now%20many%20leaders%20will%20be%20inducted%20into%20BJP%20through%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Sanjay%20Singh%20had%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731866160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Foj7vtrh8_arvind-kejriwal-kailash-gahlot_625x300_17_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-rift-grew-between-aap-and-kailash-gahlot-7042364%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20minister%20Kailash%20Gahlot's%20walkout%20from%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20was%20the%20culmination%20of%20a%20rift%20that%20had%20its%20genesis%20in%20the%20division%20of%20portfolios%20held%20by%20Manish%20Sisodia%20after%20he%20was%20arrested%20in%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-rift-grew-between-aap-and-kailash-gahlot-7042364%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Schools%20Go%20Online%2C%20No%20Entry%20For%20Trucks%20As%20Delhi%20Air%20Pollution%20Worsens%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20Delhi's%20air%20quality%20plummeting%20to%20%26quot%3Bsevere%2B%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20first%20time%20this%20season%2C%20the%20Centre's%20air%20quality%20panel%20on%20Sunday%20announced%20stricter%20pollution%20control%20measures%20for%20the%20Delhi-NCR%20under%20Stage%204%20of%20the%20Graded%20Response%20Action%20Plan%20(GRAP)%2C%20which%20will%20come%20into%20effect%20from%208%20am%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20stricter%20pollution%20control%20measures%20were%20invoked%2C%20the%20Delhi%20government%20suspended%20in-person%20classes%20for%20all%20except%20for%20students%20of%20classes%2010%20and%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWith%20the%20imposition%20of%20GRAP-4%20from%20tmrw%2C%20physical%20classes%20shall%20be%20discontinued%20for%20all%20students%2C%20apart%20from%20Class%2010%20and%2012.%20All%20schools%20will%20hold%20online%20classes%2C%20until%20further%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Atishi%20(%40AtishiAAP)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAtishiAAP%2Fstatus%2F1858180539515023764%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2017%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Environment%20Minister%20Gopal%20Rai%20will%20hold%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20Heads%20of%20Departments%20of%20all%20concerned%20departments%20tomorrow%20for%20the%20effective%20implementation%20of%20the%20GRAP%20IV%2C%20his%20office%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20restrictions%20include%20a%20ban%20on%20truck%20entry%20and%20a%20temporary%20halt%20on%20construction%20at%20public%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20AQI%20of%20Delhi%20was%20recorded%20at%20441%20(Severe)%20at%204%3A00%20PM%20today%20and%20has%20been%20gradually%20increasing%20further%20and%20has%20already%20reached%20Severe%2B%20category%2C%20as%20thc%20AQI%20clocked%20447%2C%20452%20and%20457%20at%205%3A00%20PM%2C%206%3A00%20PM%20and%207%3A0O%20PM%2C%20respectively%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Commission%20for%20Air%20Quality%20Management%20(CAQM)%2C%20the%20Centre's%20panel%20on%20Delhi-NCR%20air%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20GRAP%20for%20Delhi-NCR%20is%20divided%20into%20four%20stages%20of%20air%20quality%3A%20Stage%201%20for%20%26quot%3Bpoor%26quot%3B%20air%20quality%20(AQI%20ranging%20from%20201%20to%20300)%2C%20Stage%202%20for%20%26quot%3Bvery%20poor%26quot%3B%20air%20quality%20(AQI%20from%20301%20to%20400)%2C%20Stage%203%20for%20%26quot%3Bsevere%26quot%3B%20air%20quality%20(AQI%20from%20401%20to%20450)%2C%20and%20Stage%204%20for%20%26quot%3Bsevere%20plus%26quot%3B%20air%20quality%20(AQI%20above%20450).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20order%2C%20no%20trucks%20will%20be%20allowed%20into%20Delhi%20except%20for%20those%20carrying%20essential%20items%20or%20using%20clean%20fuel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENon-essential%20light%20commercial%20vehicles%20registered%20outside%20Delhi%20will%20also%20be%20prohibited%2C%20except%20for%20Electric%20Vehicles%20and%20CNG%20and%20BS-VI%20diesel%20o