0James%20just%20wore%20another%20salwar%20and%20went%20back%20to%20the%20rescue%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20smoke%2C%20and%20once%20the%20lights%20went%20out%2C%20we%20could%20not%20see%20anything.%20The%20entire%20staff%20brought%20out%20at%20least%2014-15%20children.%20There%20were%2011%20beds%20in%20the%20ward%20with%2023-24%20babies%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHad%20the%20lights%20not%20gone%20out%20they%20could%20have%20saved%20more%20children%2C%20Megha%20James%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20all%20happened%20very%20suddenly.%20None%20of%20us%20had%20expected%20it.%26quot%3B%20Assistant%20Nursing%20Superintendent%20Nalini%20Sood%20praised%20Megha%20James's%20valour%20and%20recounted%20bits%20from%20how%20the%20rescue%20operation%20was%20carried%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20hospital%20staff%20broke%20the%20glasses%20of%20the%20NICU%20ward%20to%20evacuate%20the%20babies.%20It%20was%20then%20Nurse%20Megha's%20salwar%20caught%20fire.%20Instead%20of%20caring%20for%20her%20safety%2C%20she%20stayed%20there%20to%20rescue%20the%20babies%20and%20handed%20them%20over%20to%20people%20outside%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENalini%20Sood%20said%20Megha%20James%20is%20currently%20undergoing%20treatment%20at%20the%20same%20medical%20college.%20She%20said%20she%20did%20not%20know%20the%20extent%20of%20her%20burns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20rescued%20babies%20were%20shifted%20to%20a%20ward%20very%20close%20to%20the%20NICU%20ward...%20When%20I%20recall%20the%20scene%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20crying%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Anshul%20Jain%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20anaesthesiology%20department%20at%20the%20medical%20college%2C%20explained%20the%20standard%20rescue%20operation%20and%20claimed%20the%20hospital%20followed%20the%20protocol%20to%20the%20T.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20triage%20process%20during%20an%20ICU%20evacuation%2C%20the%20policy%20is%20to%20evacuate%20less-affected%20patients%20first.%20The%20rationale%20behind%20this%20approach%20is%20that%20patients%20requiring%20minimal%20support%20can%20be%20relocated%20quickly%2C%20enabling%20a%20larger%20number%20of%20evacuations%20to%20be%20completed%20in%20a%20shorter%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20contrast%2C%20patients%20on%20ventilators%20or%20requiring%20high%20oxygen%20support%20demand%20more%20time%20and%20resources%20for%20evacuation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20principle%20was%20successfully%20implemented%20in%20Jhansi%2C%20playing%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20saving%20many%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Anshul%20Jain%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20newborn%20rescued%20from%20the%20fire%20died%20due%20to%20illness%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Jhansi%20District%20Magistrate%20Avinash%20Kumar%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731864060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fur6k3vj8_jhansi-fire_625x300_16_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjhansi-fire-salwar-caught-fire-but-how-jhansi-nurse-saved-over-dozen-babies-7042167%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nurse%20Megha%20James%20was%20on%20duty%20when%20the%20fire%20broke%20out%20at%20the%20Jhansi%20hospital%20and%20she%20threw%20herself%20headlong%20into%20the%20rescue%20efforts%2C%20playing%20a%20hero's%20role%20by%20saving%20several%20babies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Charli%20xcx%20Nails%20Double%20Duty%20%E2%80%98SNL%E2%80%99%20Stint%20With%20Adele%20Impersonation%2C%20Introduction%20From%20Julia%20Fox%20and%20Some%20Encouragement%20From%20Adriana%20Grande%22%2C%22conten