20targeting%20others.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20UK%20company%20has%20now%20designed%20an%20AI%20chatbot%20that%20will%20do%20it%20for%20you.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BScambaiting%26quot%3B%20is%20when%20the%20target%20of%20a%20phone%20or%20online%20scam%20realizes%20what's%20happening%20and%20plays%20along.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20waste%20as%20much%20of%20the%20scammer's%20time%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20is%20often%20hilarious%20and%20has%20given%20rise%20to%20a%20successful%20genre%20of%20online%20content%20in%20which%20users%20post%20their%20successful%20attempts%20to%20bait%20scammers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20process%2C%20however%2C%20can%20be%20time-consuming.%20So%20a%20UK%20company%20called%20Virgin%20Media%20O2%20is%20offering%20a%20solution%3A%20an%20AI%20grandmother%20named%20Daisy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20demonstration%20last%20week%2C%20the%20company%20showed%20how%20someone%20could%20deploy%20the%20AI%20chatbot%20to%20waste%20a%20scammer's%20time%20on%20their%20behalf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20state-of-the-art%20AI%20Granny's%20mission%20is%20to%20talk%20with%20fraudsters%20and%20waste%20as%20much%20of%20their%20time%20as%20possible%20with%20human-like%20rambling%20chat%20to%20keep%20them%20away%20from%20real%20people%20while%20highlighting%20the%20need%20for%20consumers%20to%20stay%20vigilant%20as%20the%20UK%20faces%20a%20fraud%20epidemic%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20is%20worldwide.%20Almost%201%20in%203%20Americans%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fonline-scams-fraud-liability-banks-government-ftc-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20victim%20of%20a%20scam%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20past%20year%2C%20with%20an%20average%20loss%20of%20%241%2C600%20a%20person%2C%20according%20to%20a%20study%20from%20IPX%2C%20a%20financial%20analysis%20firm.%20According%20to%20the%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission%2C%20consumers%20reported%20more%20than%20%2410%20billion%20in%20losses%20last%20year%20from%20online%20scams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVirgin%20Media%20O2%20says%20it%20decided%20to%20create%20Daisy%20after%20conducting%20research%20that%20showed%20that%2071%25%20of%20Brits%20wanted%20to%20retaliate%20against%20scammers%20but%20that%20most%20of%20them%20didn't%20want%20to%20spend%20the%20time%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20company%20partnered%20with%20one%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20scambaiters%20on%20YouTube%2C%20Jim%20Browning%2C%20to%20train%20the%20AI%20chatbot.%20Browning%20is%20known%20for%20pretending%20to%20be%20a%20clueless%20victim%20long%20enough%20to%20frustrate%20scammers.%20Browning%20has%20more%20than%204.3%20million%20subscribers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVirgin%20Media%20O2%20told%20BI%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20Daisy%20%26quot%3Bcombines%20various%20AI%20models%20which%20work%20together%20to%20listen%20and%20respond%20to%20fraudulent%20calls%20instantaneously%20and%20is%20so%20lifelike%20it%20has%20successfully%20kept%20numerous%20fraudsters%20on%20calls%20for%2040%20minutes%20at%20a%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDaisy%20is%20turning%20the%20tables%20on%20scammers%20%E2%80%94%20outsmarting%20and%20outmaneuvering%20them%20at%20their%20own%20cruel%20game%20simply%20by%20keeping%20them%20on%20the%20line%2C%26quot%3B%20director%20of%20fraud%20at%20Virgin%20Media%20O2%2C%20Murray%20Mackenzie%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20crucially%2C%20Daisy%20is%20also%20a%20reminder%20that%20no%20matter%20how%20persuasive%20someone%20on%20the%20other%20end%20of%20the%20phone%20may%20be%2C%20they%20aren't%20always%20who%20you%20think%20they%20are.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-grandmother-daisy-scambait-online-scams-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731862373000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673910d0fa0140cdd563e890%