0MP%20Sudha%20Murty%20has%20spoken%20of%20her%20pride%20in%20son-in-law%20Rishi%20Sunak%2C%20a%20British%20citizen%20with%20%26quot%3Bgood%20Indian%20cultural%20values%26quot%3B%20imbibed%20from%20his%20parents'%20upbringing%20in%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESudha%20Murty%20joined%20Rishi%20Sunak%20and%20her%20daughter%20Akshata%20Murty%20as%20the%20guest%20of%20honour%20at%20Bharatiya%20Vidya%20Bhavan's%20annual%20Diwali%20gala%20in%20London%20on%20Saturday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parents%20of%20the%20British%20Indian%20former%20prime%20minister%2C%20Usha%20and%20Yashvir%20Sunak%2C%20were%20also%20in%20the%20audience%20as%20Bhavan%20UK%20students%20showcased%20a%20variety%20of%20Indian%20classical%20music%20and%20dance%20forms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20always%20believe%20when%20you%20are%20abroad%2C%20your%20parents%20must%20do%20two%20things%3A%20one%20is%20good%20education%2C%20which%20gives%20you%20wings%20in%20return%20and%20you%20can%20fly%20anywhere%20and%20settle%3B%20the%20second%20is%20great%20culture%2C%20your%20origin%20which%20is%20Indian%20origin%20or%20roots%20which%20you%20can%20get%20at%20Bharatiya%20Vidya%20Bhavan%20along%20with%20your%20parents%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sudha%20Murty%2C%20delivering%20her%20keynote%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20congratulate%20Ushaji%2C%20my%20sambandhi%20and%20a%20good%20friend%20of%20mine%2C%20who%20gave%20her%20son%20Rishi%20Sunak%2C%20former%20prime%20minister%2C%20a%20great%20route%20to%20identify%20with%20the%20culture%2C%20making%20him%20a%20proud%20British%20citizen%20as%20well%20as%20%5Bhaving%5D%20good%20Indian%20cultural%20values%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20philanthropist%20went%20on%20to%20appeal%20to%20the%20British%20Indian%20community%20to%20enable%20the%20work%20of%20Bhavan%20UK's%20cultural%20activities%2C%20%26quot%3Bmentally%2C%20physically%20and%20financially%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20must%20send%20your%20children%20here%20to%20understand%20Indian%20culture%20because%20when%20you%20grow%20old%20you%20go%20towards%20your%20roots...%20that%20gap%20is%20addressed%20by%20Bharatiya%20Vidya%20Bhavan%2C%20so%20you%20have%20to%20help%20them%20in%20every%20way%20to%20survive%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20staunch%20supporter%20of%20the%20cultural%20centre%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20High%20Commissioner%20to%20the%20UK%2C%20Vikram%20Doraiswami%2C%20reflected%20upon%20Murty's%20writings%20which%20inspire%20readers%20to%20be%20true%20to%20themselves%20because%20our%20%26quot%3Borigin%20story%20matters%26quot%3B%20as%20he%20went%20on%20to%20trace%20the%20pan-Indian%20message%20of%20Diwali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Krishna%20story%20is%20relevant%20to%20Diwali%20in%20the%20south%2C%20just%20as%20the%20'Ramayana'%20story%20and%20the%20return%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20to%20Ayodhya%20from%20Lanka%20is%20connected%20to%20the%20Diwali%20story%20of%20the%20north%20and%20the%20story%20of%20Kali%20Puja%20is%20connected%20with%20the%20story%20of%20Diwali%20in%20the%20east%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDiwali%20connects%20up%20with%20the%20Sikh%20tradition%2C%20with%20the%20Jain%20and%20Buddhist%20traditions%20too.%20It%20tells%20us%20that%20light%20also%20means%20there%20is%20no%20such%20thing%20as%20a%20single%20certainty%20because%20in%20the%20light%20you%20recognise%20the%20diversity%20of%20the%20human%20condition%2C%20the%20diversity%20of%20everything%20we%20live%20with.%20So%2C%20in%20a%20world%20in%20which%20we%20spend%20our%20time%20fighting%20about%20certainties%2C%20it%20is%20a%20really%20good%20idea%20to%20look%20at%20Diwali%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20consider%20how%20so%20many%20things%20look%20differently%20in%20the%20light.%26quot%3B%20Subhanu%20Saxena%2C%20chairman%20of%20The%20Bhavan%20UK%2C%20and%20Executive%20Director%20Dr%20M.N.%20Nandakumara%20opened%20the%20event%20with%20Vedic%20chants%20as%20they%20highlighted%20the%20cultural%20centre's%20many%20achievements%20over%20the%20years%20as%20a%20centre%20of%20excellence%20in%20Indian%20arts%2C%20music%2C%20dance%2C%20Yoga%20and%20languages%2C%20offering%20over%20120%20classes%20across%2023%20different%20subject%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERishi%20Sunak%20and%20Akshata%20Murty%20presented%20mementoes%20to%20the%20team%20behind%20the%20centre's%20many%20activities%20since%20the%201970s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20students%20and%20teachers%20showcased%20their%20Kuchipudi%2C%20Kathak%20and%20Bharatanatyam%20skills%20at%20the%20annual%20Diwali%20celebration%20as%20they%20appealed%20for%20donations%20from%20the%20British%20Indian%20community%20to%20enhance%20their%20summer%20school%20and%20scholarship%20offerings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Bhavan%20UK%20is%20a%20great%20organisation%20promoting%20Indian%20culture%20and%20deserves%20our%20full%20support%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20NRI%20industrialist%20Lord%20Swraj%20Paul%2C%20one%20of%20the%20many%20supporters%20of%20the%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731861780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fk076u0vg_rishi-sunak_625x300_17_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsudha-murty-praises-son-in-law-rishi-sunaks-good-indian-cultural-values-7041811%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Well-known%20author%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Sudha%20Murty%20has%20spoken%20of%20her%20pride%20in%20son-in-law%20Rishi%20Sunak%2C%20a%20British%20citizen%20with%20%26quot%3Bgood%20Indian%20cultural%20values%26quot%3B%20imbibed%20from%20his%20parents'%20upbringing%20in%20the%20UK.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bill%20Clint