rnet%20and%20mobile%20data%20services%20in%20Manipur%20to%20be%20shut%20off%20for%20two%20days%20in%20order%20to%20bring%20the%20latest%20unrest%20under%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnti-social%20elements%20might%20use%20social%20media%20extensively%20for%20transmission%20of%20images%2C%20hate%20speech%20and%20hate%20video%20messages%20inciting%20the%20passions%20of%20the%20public%20which%20might%20have%20serious%20repercussions%20for%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20notice%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInternet%20services%20were%20shut%20down%20for%20months%20in%20Manipur%20last%20year%20during%20an%20outbreak%20of%20violence%20which%20displaced%20around%2060%2C000%20people%20from%20their%20homes%2C%20according%20to%20government%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20had%20on%20Thursday%20reimposed%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20(Special%20Powers)%20Act%20in%20Manipur's%20six%20police%20station%20areas%2C%20including%20the%20violence-hit%20Jiribam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20the%20state's%20residents%20are%20living%20in%20emergency%20shelters%2C%20still%20unable%20to%20return%20home%20due%20to%20ongoing%20tensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731858540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fklk0s8c8_amit-shah_625x300_16_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famit-shah-reviews-manipur-security-situation-amid-escalating-violence-sources-7041079%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20called%20a%20conferral%20of%20senior%20officials%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Sunday%2C%20said%20sources%2C%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20escalating%20crisis%20in%20Manipur%20-%20the%20latest%20trigger%20being%20the%20recovery%20of%20six%20bodies%20of%20people%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20kidnapped%20by%20insurgents%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famit-shah-reviews-manipur-securi