rders%2C%20but%20the%20staff%20member%20wanted%20to%20try%20to%20check%20if%20there'd%20be%20enough%20of%20each%20order%20to%20cater%20to%20everyone%20in%20the%20queue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20there%20was%20a%20chance%20of%20demand%20exceeding%20supply%2C%20they%20advised%20people%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20queue%20to%20go%20home%20and%20not%20risk%20wasting%20their%20time.%20Thankfully%2C%20we%20were%20well%20within%20the%20cutoff%20limit%20and%20didn't%20need%20to%20worry%20about%20the%20food%20running%20out%20before%20we%20ordered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2275dce06e-48b5-4509-b331-86569a39fe52%5C%22%3EThe%20samples%20we%20received%20left%20me%20wanting%20more%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20could%20smell%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freview-is-texas-roadhouse-worth-it-date-night-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edelicious%20meat%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20the%20smokers%20were%20very%20close%20to%20the%20line%2C%20which%20made%20us%20even%20more%20eager%20to%20eat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%2010%3A30%20a.m.%2C%20another%20employee%20came%20to%20hand%20out%20some%20small%20samples.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20portion%20sizes%20were%20smaller%20than%20a%20bite%2C%20the%20piece%20I%20tried%20had%20me%20salivating.%20My%20stomach%20was%20rumbling%2C%20but%20I%20knew%20we%20still%20had%20a%20few%20hours%20left%20of%20waiting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20a%20local%20reporter%20started%20asking%20a%20few%20of%20us%20why%20we%20were%20in%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20reporter%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Texas%20paper%20came%20to%20ask%20some%20tourists%20why%20they%20were%20there.%20As%20an%20Australian%2C%20I%20was%20one%20of%20the%20people%20interviewed.%20I%20joked%20I'd%20flown%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-people-make-visiting-australia-first-time-from-local-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDown%20Under%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20lunch%20just%20to%20fly%20