2C%26quot%3B%20how%20his%20frugality%20ended%20up%20being%20one%20of%20his%20best%20business%20moves%2C%20and%20the%20one%20thing%20that%20baffles%20him%20about%20%26quot%3BStranger%20Things%26quot%3B%20fans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226a36a54d-8505-4711-af23-8bd21ebd51da%5C%22%3EOn%20why%20playing%20Dr.%20Owens%20in%20'Stranger%20Things'%20was%20an%20'acting%20challenge'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223839%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Millie%20Bobby%20Brown%20as%20Eleven%20and%20Paul%20Reiser%20as%20Dr.%20Owens%20on%20%26quot%3BStranger%20Things.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67364f0dfa0140cdd5638b07%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221899%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMillie%20Bobby%20Brown%20as%20Eleven%20and%20Paul%20Reiser%20as%20Dr.%20Owens%20on%20%26quot%3BStranger%20Things.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBurke%20in%20%26quot%3BAliens%26quot%3B%20is%20one%20of%20your%20most%20notable%20performances.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20you%20were%20mostly%20known%20for%20standup%20and%20roles%20in%20%26quot%3BDiner%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BBeverly%20Hills%20Cop.%26quot%3B%20Did%20being%20in%20%26quot%3BAliens%26quot%3B%20lead%20you%20to%20be%20considered%20for%20more%20antagonist%20roles%20after%20that%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20it%20did%20open%20it%20up%20a%20bit%20because%20it%20was%20such%20a%20popular%20movie.%20I%20dunno%20about%20being%20an%20antagonist.%20Do%20I%20play%20the%20antagonist%3F%20I%20don't%20know.%20I%20like%20doing%20that.%20I%20mean%2C%20it's%20fun%20to%20be%20a%20sort%20of%20prickly%20guy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20things%20that%20was%20fun%20with%20%26quot%3BStranger%20Things%26quot%3B%20was%20it%20was%20never%20clear%20to%20me%2C%20or%20maybe%20it%20wasn't%20even%20clear%20to%20the%20creators%2C%20if%20I%20was%20a%20good%20guy%20or%20a%20bad%20guy.%20And%20I%20thought%2C%20well%2C%20that's%20a%20rea