your%20room.%20Or%20your%20interest%20in%20communicating%20with%20your%20parents%20outside%20the%20occasional%20grunt.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlso%2C%20though%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20our%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftransgender-childhood-wish-was-able-transition-child-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edaughter%20transitioned%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20right%20around%20adolescence%20really%20drove%20home%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20transitioning%2C%20while%20a%20big%20step%2C%20is%20pretty%20similar%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20other%20big%20steps%20that%20are%20fairly%20universal%20correlates%20of%20growing%20up.%20Children%20don't%20stay%20the%20same%3B%20this%20is%20a%20good%20thing%20when%20you%20can%20stop%20changing%20their%20diapers%2C%20and%20then%20maybe%20not%20as%20good%20when%20they%20no%20longer%20want%20to%20watch%20television%20with%20you%20because%20they%20are%20going%20out%20to%20see%20a%20queer%20hardcore%20band%20with%20their%20girlfriend.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20upsides%20too%2C%20though.%20We%20like%20her%20girlfriend%2C%20who%20is%20more%20willing%20to%20chat%20with%20us%20than%20our%20daughter%2C%20perhaps%20because%20we're%20not%20her%20parents.%20And%20we%20are%20proud%20of%20our%20daughter%20for%20figuring%20out%20who%20she%20is%2C%20just%20as%20many%20parents%20are%20proud%20of%20their%20kids%20for%20climbing%20up%20out%20of%20childhood%20and%20figuring%20out%20who%20they%20are%2C%20even%20if%20the%20person%20they%20are%20doesn't%20keep%20their%20room%20as%20neat%20as%20they%20once%20did.%20A%20big%20challenge%20of%20parenting%20is%20adjusting%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20children%20grow%20up%2C%20and%20that%20in%20growing%20up%2C%20they%20scramble%20your%20life%20and%20surprise%20you.%20But%20that's%20one%20of%20the%20big%20joys%20of%20parenting%2C%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3C