%3EI%20soon%20learned%20his%20name%20was%20Aram%2C%20and%20he%20had%20a%20copy%20of%20%26quot%3BLeaves%20of%20Grass%26quot%3B%20in%20his%20car%2C%20just%20like%20I%20did.%20We%20began%20corresponding%20via%20email%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-that-died-this-decade-aim-vine-moviepass-2019-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAOL%20Instant%20Messenger%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20We'd%20send%20each%20other%20creative%20emails%20of%20poetry%2C%20musings%20about%20life%2C%20or%20just%20a%20rundown%20of%20our%20day.%20We%20never%20exchanged%20photos%20or%20talked%20about%20what%20we%20looked%20like%2C%20and%20we%20had%20no%20digital%20footprint%20since%20it%20was%20the%20early%20days%20of%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20about%20a%20month%20of%20emails%20and%20chats%2C%20I%20told%20him%20I%20wanted%20to%20talk%20on%20the%20phone.%20I%20wanted%20to%20hear%20his%20voice%2C%20his%20laugh%2C%20how%20he%20said%20my%20name.%20It%20was%20the%20next%20step%20in%20getting%20to%20know%20each%20other%20and%20marked%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20our%20relationship.%20From%20that%20moment%20on%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-restored-my-marriage-by-setting-boundaries-about-work-talk-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewe%20talked%20every%20day%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20I%20even%20chatted%20with%20his%20mom%2C%20and%20he%20with%20my%20family.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENeither%20of%20us%20had%20a%20cellphone.%20Our%20hourslong%20phone%20calls%20turned%20into%20%24300%20to%20400%20phone%20bills.%20We'd%20often%20talk%20late%20into%20the%20evening%20%E2%80%94%20and%20if%20I%20fell%20asleep%2C%20he'd%20stay%20on%20the%20line.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20one%20such%20call%2C%20he%20realized%20I%20was%20the%20one%20he%20wanted%20to%20be%20with%20forever.%20He%20heard%20me%20breathing%2C%20woke%20me%20up%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%2C%20and%20asked%20me%20to%20marry%20him.%20This%20was%20about%20three%20months%20into%20our%20daily%20phone%20calls.%20I%20was%20in%20my%20mid-20s%2C%20he%20was%20in%20his%20early%2030s.%20It%20was%20a%20first%20for%20both%20of%20us.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20there%20was%20no%20engagement%20ring%2C%20and%20we%20still%20had%20no%20idea%20what%20each%20other%20looked%20like%2C%20we%20took%20our%20relationship%20seriously.%20We%20committed%20to%20staying%20exclusive%2C%20living%20apart%20together%20for%20about%20a%20year.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20families%20thought%20we%20were%20a%20little%20crazy%2C%20but%20they%20went%20along%20with%20it%20and%20ultimately%20gave%20us%20their%20blessing.%20It%20helped%20that%20we%20took%20our%20time%20and%20didn't%20rush.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c5d8be5c-ebcf-494d-acae-9ad57cc36100%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20weren't%20each%20other's%20type%20but%20that%20didn't%20matter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20never%20exchanged%20photos%20until%20just%20days%20before%20we%20met%20at%20the%20Detroit%20airport%20on%20January%2023%2C%202001.%20It%20was%20a%20surreal%20and%20hilarious%20moment%20we%20still%20laugh%20and%20reminisce%20about.%20Even%20though%20we%20believed%20looks%20didn't%20matter%2C%20we%20didn't%20exactly%20fit%20each%20other's%20%26quot%3Bideal%26quot%3B%20in%20terms%20of%20physical%20appearance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUp%20until%20that%20point%2C%20I%20was%20mostly%20attracted%20to%20skinny%20blonde%20guys%2C%20and%20he%20thought%20California%20girls%20looked%20like%20the%20women%20on%20%26quot%3BBaywatch.%26quot%3B%20Well%2C%20I'm%20a%20short%20Latina%2C%20and%20he's%20a%20tall%2C%20husky%20Armenian.%20Fortunately%2C%20when%20we%20met%2C%20the%20love%20was%20already%20there%2C%20and%20no%20physical%20trait%20was%20about%20to%20change%20that.%20He%20thought%20I%20was%20beautiful%2C%20and%20I%20told%20him%20he%20could've%20been%20a%20Cyclops%2C%20and%20I%20would've%20still%20loved%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20we%20fell%20in%20love%20quite%20quickly%2C%20we%20considered%20engagement%20its%20own%20form%20of%20marriage%20and%20didn't%20tie%20the%20knot%20until%2014%20years%20later.%20We%20decided%20to%20make%20our%20relationship%20official%20in%20May%202015%2C%20surrounded%20by%20loved%20ones.%20It%20ended%20up%20being%20the%20happiest%20day%20of%20our%20lives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20more%20than%2020%20years%20of%20making%20each%20other%20laugh%20and%20supporting%20each%20other%20through%20life's%20most%20joyful%20moments%20and%20painful%20losses%2C%20I%20can%20say%20absolutely%20yes%2C%20love%20is%20blind.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20not%20always%20what%20you%20expect%20it%20to%20be%20%E2%80%94%20it%20can%20be%20so%20much%20better.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgot-engaged-without-seeing-each-other-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731846242000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67364739ede4eeae3927a1eb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgot-engaged-without-seeing-each-other-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We%20met%20on%20an%20online%20forum%20and%20got%20engaged%20before%20sharing%20photos%20of%20each%20other.%20We%20are%20still%20happy%20together%2020%20years%20later.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Mar%20Yvette)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A30%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgot-engaged-without-seeing-each-other-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Inside%20%26quot%3BLord%20Of%20Drugs%26quot%3B%20Haji%20Salim's%20Global%20Narcotics%20Network%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHaji%20Salim%2C%20known%20infamously%20as%20%26quot%3BLord%20of%20Drugs%2C%26quot%3B%20has%20earned%20a%20notorious%20reputation%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20influential%20figures%20in%20global%20drug%20trafficking.%20Operating%20primarily%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20he%20leads%20an%20expansive%20criminal%20network%20responsible%20for%20smuggling%20large%20quantities%20of%20heroin%2C%20methamphetamine%2C%20and%20other%20illicit%20substances%20into%20India%20and%20beyond.%20The%20Narcotics%20Control%20Bureau%20(NCB)%20of%20India%20has%20launched%20significant%20operations%20to%20dismantle%20Salim's%20empire%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanti-drugs-agency-launches-major-op-to-track-down-lord-of-drugs-haji-salim-7037476%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BOperation%20Sagar%20Manthan%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0emerging%20as%20a%20key%20effort%20in%20the%20fight%20against%20his%20narcotics%20syndicate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Rise%20Of%20Haji%20Salim%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanti-drugs-agency-launches-major-op-to-track-down-lord-of-drugs-haji-salim-7037476%5C%22%3EHaji%20Salim%3C%2Fa%3E's%20criminal%20activities%20came%20into%20the%20spotlight%20in%202015%20when%20a%20major%20drug%20consignment%20linked%20to%20him%20was%20seized%20in%20Kerala.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20authorities%20have%20traced%20numerous%20large-scale%20drug%20busts%20back%20to%20him%2C%20making%20his%20name%20synonymous%20with%20narcotics%20smuggling%20in%20India.%20He%20is%20also%20closely%20connected%20to%20the%20infamous%20fugitive%20gangster%20Dawood%20Ibrahim%2C%20as%20the%20two%20are%20said%20to%20be%20neighbours%20in%20Pakistan's%20Balochistan%20province.%20Salim%20reportedly%20runs%20his%20operations%20with%20the%20support%20of%20Pakistan's%20intelligence%20agency%2C%20ISI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOperation%20Sagar%20Manthan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20growing%20threat%20posed%20by%20Haji%20Salim's%20cartel%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20launched%20%26quot%3BOperation%20Sagar%20Manthan%26quot%3B%20earlier%20this%20year.%20The%20operation%20is%20a%20collaborative%20effort%20between%20the%20NCB%2C%20Indian%20Navy%2C%20Indian%20Coast%20Guard%2C%20and%20Gujarat%20Police's%20Anti-Terrorism%20Squad%20(ATS).%20The%20primary%20objective%20is%20to%20disrupt%20maritime%20drug%20trafficking%2C%20which%20Salim%20heavily%20relies%20on.%20So%20far%2C%20the%20operation%20has%20led%20to%20the%20seizure%20of%20around%203%2C400%20kg%20of%20narcotics%2C%20and%20multiple%20arrests%2C%20including%20citizens%20from%20Iran%20and%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20operation%20focuses%20on%20intercepting%20shipments%20that%20are%20sent%20via%20sea%20routes%2C%20a%20method%20Salim%20has%20perfected.%20His%20drugs%20are%20often%20packed%20with%20code%20words%20like%20%26quot%3B777%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3B555%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3B999%2C%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%9Cscorpions%E2%80%9D%20and%20%26quot%3Bflying%20horse%26quot%3B%20to%20avoid%20detection.%20The%20consignments%20typically%20start%20from%20Iran%2C%20pass%20through%20countries%20like%20Malaysia%2C%20Afghanistan%2C%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20and%20are%20finally%20delivered%20to%20coastal%20cities%20in%20India%2C%20such%20as%20Gujarat%20and%20Kerala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BRaktbeej%26quot%3B%3A%20Haji%20Salim's%20Code%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalim's%20cartel%20is%20so%20powerful%20that%20he%20has%20been%20named%20%26quot%3BRaktbeej%26quot%3B%20(meaning%20%26quot%3Bthe%20seed%20of%20blood%26quot%3B)%20in%20reference%20to%20his%20dominance%20in%20drug%20trafficking%20in%20India.%20He%20is%20responsible%20for%20about%2070%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20drug%20smuggling%20across%20India's%20seas.%20His%20syndicate%20operates%20globally%2C%20with%20links%20to%20countries%20such%20as%20Mauritius%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20New%20Zealand%2C%20America%2C%20and%20even%20Afghanistan.%20Salim%20uses%20unemployed%20youth%20from%20Balochistan%20as%20his%20foot%20soldiers%2C%20drawing%20them%20into%20the%20drug%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20his%20wide-reaching%20operations%2C%20very%20little%20is%20known%20about%20Salim%20personally.%20Authorities%20only%20have%20an%20old%20photograph%20of%20him%2C%20and%20details%20about%20his%20life%20remain%20scarce.%20His%20network%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20bolstered%20by%20the%20ISI%2C%20which%20helps%20him%20ensure%20that%20his%20operations%20remain%20secure%20and%20undisturbed%20by%20international%20law%20enforcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHigh-Profile%20Arrests%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20months%2C%20the%20NCB%20has%20made%20significant%20progress%20in%20curbing%20Salim's%20narcotics%20shipments.%20The%20operation%2C%20%26quot%3BSagar%20Manthan-4%2C%26quot%3B%20resulted%20in%20the%20seizure%20of%20700%20kg%20of%20methamphetamine%20off%20the%20Gujarat%20coast.%20The%20authorities%20had%20received%20intelligence%20about%20an%20unregistered%20ship%20carrying%20drugs%2C%20and%20once%20it%20entered%20Indian%20waters%2C%20the%20NCB%2C%20Navy%2C%20and%20ATS%20launched%20a%20coordinated%20operation%20to%20intercept%20it.%20During%20this%20bust%2C%20eight%20foreign%20nationals%2C%20believed%20to%20be%20Iranians%2C%20were%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20have%20also%20made%20arrests%20of%20Pakistani%20nationals%20linked%20to%20Salim's%20drug%20pipeline.%20Salim's%20operation%20stretches%20far%20beyond%20India's%20borders%2C%20with%20his%20syndicate's%20reach%20affecting%20countries%20across%20Asia%2C%20Africa%2C%20and%20Western%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCB%20remains%20committed%20to%20dismantling%20Haji%20Salim's%20narcotics%20empire.%20With%20continued%20intelligence-sharing%20and%20coordination%20between%20international%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%2C%20efforts%20to%20break%20the%20syndicate%