.%20Meanwhile%2C%20rice%20farming%2C%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20fallback%20option%2C%20offered%20meagre%20profits%20and%20an%20unsustainable%20livelihood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20vision%20to%20change%20the%20face%20of%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20cultivation%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Manoj%20Kumar%20spent%20a%20decade%20researching%20ways%20to%20make%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%20%3C%2Fem%3Efarming%20more%20efficient%2C%20sustainable%2C%20and%20less%20labour-intensive.%20One%20of%20his%20breakthroughs%20was%20proving%20that%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20could%20thrive%20in%20water%20as%20shallow%20as%2030%20cm%2C%20contrary%20to%20the%20traditional%20belief%20that%20five%20to%20six%20feet%20was%20necessary.%20This%20discovery%20allowed%20farmers%20to%20grow%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20like%20any%20other%20crop%20in%20fields%2C%20reducing%20dependence%20on%20deep%2C%20flood-prone%20ponds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Kumar%20also%20developed%20a%20high-yielding%20variety%20of%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20called%20%E2%80%98Swarna%20Vaidehi%3Cem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20high-yielding%20variety%20of%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E.%20This%20variety%20adapted%20well%20to%20local%20conditions%20and%20significantly%20increased%20productivity.%20Additionally%2C%20techniques%20like%20nursery%20raising%20(growing%20seedlings%20separately%20before%20transplanting)%20and%20line%20planting%20(organised%20sowing%20in%20rows)%20were%20introduced.%20These%20methods%20reduced%20seed%20requirements%20and%20improved%20yields%2C%20making%20farming%20more%20efficient.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOvercoming%20the%20flood%20challenge%20with%20innovative%20net%20fencing%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFloods%20have%20long%20been%20a%20major%20threat%20to%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20farming%2C%20often%20destroying%20entire%20crops.%20Dr%20Kumar%20tackled%20this%20issue%20by%20introducing%20net%20fencing%2C%20a%20simple%20yet%20effective%20solution.%20It%20involves%20installing%20mesh%20barriers%20around%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%20%3C%2Fem%3Efields%20to%20protect%20crops%20from%20being%20washed%20away%20by%20floodwaters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fimage_11zon-1731671497.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mesh%20barriers%20around%20makhana%20fields%20safeguard%20crops%20from%20flood%20damage%2C%20ensuring%20a%20secure%20harvest.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fimage_11zon-1731671497.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fimage_11zon-1731671497-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fimage_11zon-1731671497-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fimage_11zon-1731671497-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fimage_11zon-1731671497-1200x675.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fimage_11zon-1731671497-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-380419%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFloods%20threaten%20makhana%20crops%2C%20but%20innovative%20solutions%20like%20net%20fencing%20provide%20protection.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EImage%20Courtesy%20PTC%20NEWS%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20innovation%20made%20it%20possible%20to%20cultivate%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20areas%20previously%20considered%20too%20risky.%20With%20the%20combination%20of%20shallow%20water%20cultivation%20and%20flood%20protection%2C%20Dr%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20methods%20have%20forever%20changed%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20farming%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20story%20of%20reaping%20rewards%20with%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%20%3C%2Fem%3Efarming%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhirendra%20Kumar%2C%20a%20farmer%20from%20Belwara%20village%20in%20Darbhanga%2C%20is%20a%20prime%20example%20of%20the%20benefits%20of%20Dr%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20innovations.%20For%20years%2C%20Dhirendra%20grew%20rice%2C%20earning%20only%20Rs%2020%2C000%20to%2025%2C000%20per%20hectare.%20Frequent%20floods%20often%20wiped%20out%20his%20crops%2C%20leaving%20him%20disheartened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20Dhirendra%20attended%20a%20%E2%80%98Farmer-Scientist%20Interaction%20cum%20Field%20Day%E2%80%99%20organised%20by%20NRCM%2C%20where%20he%20learned%20about%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20farming.%20Inspired%20by%20the%20crop%E2%80%99s%20potential%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20switch%20from%20rice%20to%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20cultivation%20on%20his%20three-hectare%20plot%2C%20thus%20becoming%20a%20key%20case%20study%20of%20Dr%20Kumar.%20With%20technical%20guidance%20from%20NRCM%20and%20Krishi%20Vigyan%20Kendra%20(KVK)%2C%20he%20planted%20Swarna%20Vaidehi%20seeds%20in%20a%20nursery%20and%20later%20transplanted%20them%20into%20his%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20initial%20challenges%20with%20nutrient%20management%2C%20Dhirendra%20harvested%2048%20quintals%20of%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20first%20season%2C%20earning%20a%20gross%20income%20of%20Rs%205.28%20lakhs%20and%20a%20net%20income%20of%20Rs%202.58%20lakhs.%20This%20was%20a%20dramatic%20improvement%20compared%20to%20the%20Rs%2060%2C000%20he%20earned%20from%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F324920%2Fbrothers-biodegradable-animal-friendly-rice-agri-waste-tableware-cutlery-plates-glass%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20rice%20farming%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20the%20same%20land%20in%20previous%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPolythene%20lining%20as%20a%20simple%20solution%20to%20water%20management%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20technique%20that%20further%20boosted%20Dhirendra%E2%80%99s%20success%20was%20polythene%20lining%20to%20prevent%20water%20loss%20from%20lateral%20seepage.%20Traditionally%2C%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20farmers%20struggled%20to%20maintain%20consistent%20water%20levels%20in%20their%20fields%2C%20especially%20during%20the%20dry%20pre-monsoon%20months%20(March%20to%20May).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Kumar%20recommended%20using%20100-micron%20polythene%20sheets%20to%20seal%20the%20bunds%20(field%20barriers).%20This%20simple%2C%20low-cost%20solution%20minimised%20water%20seepage%2C%20reducing%20the%20need%20for%20frequent%20irrigation.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20Dhirendra%20saved%20both%20water%20and%20costs%2C%20making%20his%20farming%20process%20more%20sustainable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20690px)%20100vw%2C%20690px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fimage-3_11zon-1731671481.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22690%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20farmer%20harvesting%20makhana%20from%20a%20well-managed%20field%2C%20showcasing%20the%20increased%20yields%20and%20improved%20income%20resulting%20from%20modern%20farming%20techniques.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fimage-3_11zon-1731671481.jpg%20690w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fimage-3_11zon-1731671481-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fimage-3_11zon-1731671481-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fimage-3_11zon-1731671481-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-380418%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22388%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFarmers%20are%20increasing%20income%20and%20yields%20with%20improved%20makhana%20farming%20methods.%3Cbr%3EImage%20courtesy%20India%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20game-changer%20for%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20farmers%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20like%20Dhirendra%2C%20many%20farmers%20across%20Bihar%20have%20embraced%20Dr%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20innovations%2C%20transforming%20their%20livelihoods.%20With%20flood-resistant%20practices%2C%20shallow%20water%20cultivation%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F327478%2Fashwin-sawant-low-cost-hydroponics-model-helps-farmers-grow-fodder-save-water%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewater-saving%20techniques%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20polythene%20%3Cem%3Ebund%20%3C%2Fem%3Elining%2C%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20farming%20has%20become%20a%20viable%20and%20profitable%20option%20for%20farmers%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Swarna%20Vaidehi%20variety%E2%80%99s%20high%20yield%20and%20the%20growing%20global%20demand%20for%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20have%20opened%20new%20markets%20for%20farmers.%20The%20GI%20tag%20for%20Mithila%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20ensures%20premium%20prices%20for%20high-quality%20produce%2C%20further%20boosting%20farmer%20incomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20water-intensive%20crops%20like%20rice%2C%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20thrives%20in%20shallow%20water%20and%20is%20better%20suited%20to%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20unpredictable%20weather%2C%20reducing%