.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrika%20has%20also%20employed%20two%20women%20%E2%80%94%20Akriti%20Subba%20and%20Rakhi%20Gurung%20%E2%80%94%20to%20help%20her%20in%20her%20mission.%20%E2%80%9CI%20pay%20them%20a%20very%20modest%20salary.%20They%20are%20also%20die-hard%20animal%20lovers%20and%20have%20been%20incredibly%20supportive%2C%20reaching%20out%20to%20me%20to%20join%20the%20mission.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98If%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20love%20them%2C%20at%20least%20don%E2%80%99t%20hurt%20them%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrika%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20align%20with%20a%20broader%20movement%20in%20India%20to%20prevent%20cruelty%20towards%20stray%20animals%2C%20particularly%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20issued%20directives%20urging%20municipalities%20to%20treat%20stray%20dogs%20humanely%2C%20making%20provisions%20for%20their%20sterilisation%2C%20and%20calling%20for%20laws%20to%20protect%20them%20from%20harm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fawbi.gov.in%2Fuploads%2Fregulations%2F167956418266ABC%2520Rule%25202023.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnimal%20Birth%20Control%20(ABC)%20Rules%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20notified%20by%20the%20Central%20Government%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Cruelty%20to%20Animals%20Act%2C%201960%20%E2%80%94%20mandating%20the%20sterilisation%20and%20immunisation%20of%20stray%20dogs%20by%20local%20authorities%2C%20also%20explicitly%20creates%20provisions%20for%20the%20humane%20treatment%20of%20stray%20animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20prohibiting%20the%20killing%20of%20dogs%2C%20the%20ABC%20Rules%2C%202023%2C%20also%20prevent%20the%20relocation%20of%20any%20stray%20dog%20from%20their%20areas%20of%20residence.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20Ru