%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-05-at-22.31.06-1-1731592372-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-379980%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22780%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShanthini%20and%20Ganeshan%20have%20distributed%20over%2010%2C000%20nest%20boxes%20across%20schools%20in%20Chennai%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ET%20Mohanalakshmi%2C%20a%20dedicated%20Botany%20teacher%20at%20KC%20Sankaralinga%20Nadar%20Higher%20Secondary%20School%2C%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20Ganesh%2C%20are%20also%20deeply%20involved%20in%20the%20Koodugal%20Nest%20project.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20home%2C%20we%20have%20a%20large%20neem%20tree.%20When%20I%20first%20learned%20about%20Koodugal%20Nest%2C%20I%20got%20two%20sparrow%20nest%20boxes%20and%20installed%20them.%20Soon%20after%2C%20I%20was%20thrilled%20to%20see%20sparrows%20visiting%20the%20tree.%20Now%2C%20I%20have%20ten%20sparrow%20nests%2C%20and%20I%20wake%20up%20every%20morning%20to%20the%20sound%20of%20birds%20chirping%20at%204-5%20am%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ganesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKoodugal%20Nest%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20have%20not%20gone%20unnoticed.%20In%202023%2C%20the%20NGO%20received%20the%20prestigious%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Leadership%20Award%20from%20the%20World%20CSR%20Congress.%20This%20recognition%20came%20as%20a%20result%20of%20their%20dedication%20to%20environmental%20conservation%20and%20the%20significant%20impact%20they%20have%20made%20in%20the%20communities%20they%20serve.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20in%202024%2C%20the%20trust%20was%20honoured%20with%20the%20Inspiro%20Award%20by%20Agilisium%20Consulting%20for%20its%20outstanding%20contribution%20to%20conservation%20and%20education.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Koodugal%20Nest%20continues%20to%20grow%20and%20reach%20more%20people%2C%20its%20mission%20expands%20beyond%20ju