Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20spark%20behind%20LaunchPad%3A%20A%20platform%20for%20young%20entrepreneurs%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAryan%E2%80%99s%20journey%20to%20LaunchPad%20began%20long%20before%20he%20set%20out%20to%20build%20his%20first%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20traces%20his%20love%20for%20creation%20back%20to%20childhood%2C%20recalling%20how%20he%20used%20to%20make%20intricate%20origami%20figures%20when%20he%20was%20nine.%20As%20he%20grew%20older%2C%20he%20began%20to%20experiment%20with%20building%20websites%20and%20apps.%20By%20Classes%209%20and%2010%2C%20Aryan%20was%20fully%20immersed%20in%20the%20world%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332593%2Fdesign-medical-devices-innovation-nid-harvard-student-save-lives-chennai-siddharth%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edesign%20and%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20fueled%20by%20the%20subjects%20that%20were%20offered%20through%20his%20school%E2%80%99s%20International%20Baccalaureate%20(IB)%20curriculum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20his%20experiences%2C%20Aryan%20discovered%20not%20only%20his%20passion%20for%20creation%20but%20also%20the%20significant%20challenges%20that%20came%20with%20it.%20While%20working%20on%20projects%20%E2%80%94%20like%20an%20app%20for%20senior%20citizens%20and%20a%20task%20management%20website%20for%20IB%20students%20%E2%80%94%20he%20faced%20numerous%20obstacles%2C%20particularly%20around%20the%20lack%20of%20resources%20that%20spoke%20to%20his%20requirement%20as%20a%20young%20creator.%20%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20there%20was%20a%20gap%20in%20the%20resources%20available%20for%20people%20like%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aryan%20reflects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%202598px)%20100vw%2C%202598px%5C%22%2