20and%20skills%20with%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20musicians%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20culminated%20in%20the%20creation%20of%2050%20episodes%20of%20%3Cem%3EMehfil-e-Rajasthan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20featuring%20around%20110%20artists.%20Some%20of%20these%20episodes%20are%20now%20available%20on%20Spotify%2C%20bringing%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20folk%20music%20to%20a%20broader%20audience.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20just%20happy%20to%20be%20a%20catalyst%3B%20I%20connected%20the%20dots%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sharon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20fortunate%20enough%20to%20experience%20Rajasthani%20folk%20music%20live%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20an%20unmistakable%20moment%20when%20your%20ears%20immediately%20perk%20up.%20This%20art%20form%20has%20been%20perfected%20over%20generations%2C%20so%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20tradition%20that%20it%20resonates%20through%20your%20very%20bones.%20It%20feels%20as%20if%20the%20artists%2C%20singing%20with%20heads%20held%20high%2C%20are%20not%20performing%20for%20the%20audience%2C%20but%20singing%20directly%20to%20a%20higher%20power%20in%20the%20sky.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20only%20took%20one%20Shri%20Ravi%20Shankar%20%3Cem%3Eji%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20extend%20the%20sitar%E2%80%99s%20influence%20for%20another%20century.%20Similarly%2C%20it%20will%20only%20take%20a%20few%20properly%20trained%20and%20passionate%20young%20people%20to%20revive%20the%20rich%20music%20of%20Rajasthan%20and%20ensure%20its%20survival%20for%20generations%20to%20come%2C%E2%80%9D%20assures%20Bhati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Govind%20Singh%20Bhati%20and%20Sharon%20Genevive%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731072652000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D375518%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20world%20where%20traditional%20art%20forms%20are%20fading%20away%2C%20Govind%20Singh%20Bhati%20and%20Sharon%20Genevive%20are%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20revive%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20folk%20musical%20heritage.%20Through%20their%20one%20of%20a%20kind%20programme%2C%20Lok%20Sangeet%20Shala%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20empowering%20young%20artists%20from%20folk%20communities%20to%20learn%20and%20celebrate%20their%20cultural%20identity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Hemlata%20Chouhan%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22JEE%202025%20Now%20Allows%20Three%20Attempts%20%E2%80%93%20Here%E2%80%99s%20a%20Topper%E2%80%99s%20Guide%20To%20Make%20the%20Most%20of%20It%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20significant%20update%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F297383%2Fmumbai-ojas-maheshwari-with-hearing-impairment-tops-iit-jee-advanced-shares-strategy-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJEE%20Advanced%20aspirants%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(IIT)%20Kanpur%20has%20announced%20that%2C%20starting%20in%202025%2C%20students%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20attempt%20the%20prestigious%20exam%20three%20times%20over%20three%20consecutive%20years.%20This%20marks%20a%20vital%20change%20from%20the%20earlier%20limit%20of%20two%20attempts%20in%20two%20consecutive%20years%2C%20which%20had%20been%20the%20standard%20for%20many%20years.%20It%20also%20gives%20students%20an%20additional%20chance%20to%20secure%20admission%20into%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20top%20engineering%20colleges%2C%20the%20IITs.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20potential%20to%20turn%20opportunities%20into%20success%20is%20best%20exemplified%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F334571%2Fkalpit-veerwal-jee-main-topper-launches-education-startup-iit-bombay-placement-package%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKalpit%20Veerwal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20inspiring%20success%20stories%20of%20JEE%20Mains.%20The%20first%20student%20to%20ever%20score%20a%20perfect%20360%2F360%20in%20the%20exam%2C%20Kalpit%E2%80%99s%20achievement%20not%20only%20earned%20him%20the%20All%20India%20Rank%201%20(AIR%201)%20in%20JEE%20Mains%202017%2C%20but%20also%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20a%20remarkable%20career.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20graduating%20with%20a%20degree%20in%20computer%20science%20from%20IIT%20Bombay%20in%202021%2C%20Kalpit%20went%20on%20to%20become%20an%20entrepreneur%20and%20investor%2C%20leading%20his%20successful%20startup%20AcadBoost%2C%20which%20focuses%20on%20online%20education%2C%20software%2C%20and%20email%20marketing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20his%20entrepreneurial%20ventures%2C%20Kalpit%20is%20an%20active%20mentor%20and%20advisor%20to%20several%20startups%2C%20helping%20students%20and%20young%20professionals%20in%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332971%2Fbrillio-national-stem-learning-challenge-government-schools-rural-india-science-labs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeducational%20and%20career%20pursuits%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Through%20his%20platform%2C%20he%20also%20shares%20valuable%20content%20on%20exam%20preparation%2C%20business%20growth%2C%20and%20career-building%20strategies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEssential%20advice%20for%20JEE%20aspirants%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20practical%20and%20insightful%20tips%20from%20Kalpit%20Veerwal%20that%20he%20believes%20are%20essential%20for%20cracking%20the%20JEE%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Build%20consistency%20in%20study%20routine%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20piece%20of%20advice%20I%E2%80%99d%20give%20is%20to%20be%20consistent%20in%20your%20studies%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kalpit%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20He%20stresses%20that%20consistent%20study%20is%20more%20effective%20than%20short%2C%20intense%20bursts%20of%20effort.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20students%20who%20study%20regularly%2C%20even%20for%20three%20to%20four%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20tend%20to%20outperform%20those%20who%20alternate%20between%20intense%20study%20sessions%20and%20periods%20of%20inactivity.%20The%20focus%20should%20be%20on%20sticking%20to%20a%20daily%20routine%20to%20steadily%20build%20your%20knowledge%20over%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Focus%20on%20problem-solving%20over%20theory%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKalpit%20advises%2C%20%E2%80%9CReading%20theory%20is%20important%2C%20but%20practice%20makes%20perfect.%20The%20exam%20is%20all%20about%20solving%20problems.%E2%80%9D%20Since%20the%20JEE%20is%20a%20test%20of%20application%20rather%20than%20knowledge%2C%20he%20recommends%20solving%20as%20many%20problems%20as%20possible%20to%20deeply%20understand%20the%20concepts%20and%20sharpen%20your%20ability%20to%20tackle%20a%20variety%20of%20questions%20under%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Revise%20frequently%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20chapter%20must%20be%20revised%20at%20least%20five%20to%20six%20times%20before%20the%20exam%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kalpit.%20He%20believes%20that%20regular%20revision%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20habits%20for%20any%20top%20scorer.%20Revisiting%20each%20chapter%20several%20times%20throughout%20the%20year%20helps%20reinforce%20your%20memory%20and%20solidify%20understanding.%20Kalpit%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20revised%20chapters%20multiple%20times%20to%20ensure%20nothing%20was%20left%20to%20chance%2C%20and%20I%20believe%20students%20should%20also%20do%20the%20same.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Develop%20and%20practise%20a%20clear%20strategy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKalpit%20suggests%20that%20students%20should%20develop%20their%20exam%20strategy%20well%20in%20advance%20of%20the%20big%20day.%20%E2%80%9CSolve%20plenty%20of%20test%20papers%20at%20home%2C%20at%20your%20own%20pace%2C%20and%20identify%20which%20subjects%20come%20more%20naturally%20to%20you.%20This%20will%20help%20you%20decide%20which%20ones%20to%20tackle%20first%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20advises.%20It%E2%80%99s%20crucial%20to%20know%20how%20much%20time%20to%20allocate%20to%20each%20section%2C%20when%20to%20skip%20difficult%20questions%2C%20and%20how%20to%20adapt%20your%20approach%20based%20on%20the%20difficulty%20level%20of%20the%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-07-at-15.13.20-1-1731054457-500x495-1-1731055728.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-07-at-15.13.20-1-1731054457-500x495-1-1731055728.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-07-at-15.13.20-1-1731054457-500x495-1-1731055728-300x297.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-07-at-15.13.20-1-1731054457-500x495-1-1731055728-150x149.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-07-at-15.13.20-1-1731054457-500x495-1-1731055728-96x96.jpeg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-375474%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22495%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element